|-----------|------|---------------|----------|
| `client:load` | ✅ | Page load | Critical interactive |
| `client:idle` | ✅ | Browser idle | Analytics, ads |
| `client:visible` | ✅ | Scroll into view | Below-fold content |
| `client:only="react"` | ❌ | Page load | Browser-only APIs |

